  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15632/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<div>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\tSince I am just back from travelling in three provinces of Northeast China, I would like to talk about the topic on Tourism. In recent years, the industry of Chinese tourism has developed quite fast and the behavior of tourists could impact the local spots or culture to some extent.</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t1. What are the advantages in respecting local customs in travelling?<br />\n\t\t2. What are the drawbacks of international tourism?<br />\n\t\t3. What are the actions should be taken in preventing the bad behavior of tourists in damaging the local circumstance?</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\tTravelling is a way to relax stress from <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/intensive\" target=\"_blank\">intensive</a> study or work, and it helps to broaden the horizons. From my journey to three provinces in Northeast China, I am so amazed by the masterpiece of nature in Changbai Mountain and the sharp difference in the country border between China and North Korea. Respecting the local customs is to experience the different cultures and try something special apart from what we know in daily life. The <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/formation\" target=\"_blank\">formation</a> of local customs has gone through a long period of time and it means quite much to inhabitants. Showing the respect is not only a polite way to build a good image of ourselves, but also a friendly way to adapt the local circumstance.</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t游客尊重当地风俗的好处：<br />\n\t\tA certain degree of tourists' conformity to the local customs and behavior is still necessary. For one thing, this helps tourists avoid many inconveniences and conflicts during their trips abroad. For instance, Asian tourists would be spared the embarrassment of irritating their servers if they are well-informed about and follow the custom of tipping in an American restaurant. Likewise, Western travelers may avoid being highly obtrusive if they make it a point to remain calm and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/solemn\" target=\"_blank\">solemn</a> in an Asian place of worship. Moreover, efforts to adopt the local customs and behavior enable foreign tourists to better appreciate and identify with the local cultural heritage such as rites, rituals, folklore and even handicrafts.<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t国际旅游业的坏处:<br />\n\t\tInternational tourism may carry certain drawbacks socially and environmentally. Specifically, the influx of tourists may constitute an intrusion upon the lives of many local inhabitants. It is universally acknowledged that tourism is a manifestation of the human desire for variety and for exploration. As a consequence, some snooping and prying on the part of international tourists is inevitable, which may in turn render locals disconcerted and apprehensive. Moreover, vast touring populations between countries may severely undermine <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/biodiversity\" target=\"_blank\">biodiversity</a> and ecological <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/equilibrium\" target=\"_blank\">equilibrium</a>. The trail of non-biodegradable litter international tourists leave behind them and the vast amounts of fossil fuel consumed in transportation pose grave environmental threats to the tourist destinations and beyond.</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/771971/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a><br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t<br />\n\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p517697/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p517697\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p517874/\">美剧中的亚洲面孔 你认得出他们吗?</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518419/\">时尚贴士：怎样穿衣服最显瘦</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p519168/\">乔治王子长这样？电脑合成少年照</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p517448/\">十分钟改变法：十分钟就能做好的事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518729/\">破产姐妹笔记105：爷们点英语怎么说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p427945/\">从零基础到英语达人：新概念帮你轻松搞定！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p519070/\">总是觉得累？7个小贴士恢复活力</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p517619/\">智慧的声音：8句发人深省的名言</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518035/\">英国小王子首亮相 “还好长得像妈妈”</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
