  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201307/d7d1e84521fc44e18b72ff3edb208a06.jpg\" style=\"height: 318px; width: 460px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《美剧天坛秀》节目是沪江部落一档模仿类节目，目的在于提升大家的英语口语水平，在轻松看美剧的同时锻炼大家的口语能力。积极参与的童鞋还会得到主持的专业点评哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15632/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>原录音：</strong><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p516751\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>原文：</strong>L:We're not <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/supposed\" target=\"_blank\">supposed</a> to talk, remember?<br />\n\tR:Oh, I had to. I -- your mother came to see me, and she mentioned something about why you left me all those years ago.<br />\n\tL:Oh. Yes, well, she made me an offer I couldn't <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/refuse\" target=\"_blank\">refuse</a>, and I wasn't strong enough then.<br />\n\tR:Why didn't you tell me?<br />\n\tL:Oh, come on. You never would have understood.<br />\n\tR:But if I had known you hadn't <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/actually\" target=\"_blank\">actually</a> left me for -- for him, I - I... I mean, maybe --<br />\n\tL:Listen, don't. Don't. Don't say it. Don't even think it.<br />\n\tR:I can't help myself. I never should have let you... Let me go.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>重点单词发音讲解：</strong></p>\n<div>\n\tsupposed</div>\n<div>\n\t英[səˈpəʊzd] 美[səˈpoʊzd]</div>\n<div>\n\tadj. 假定的；被信以为真的<br />\n\tv. suppose的过去式和过去分词<br />\n\t&nbsp;</div>\n<div>\n\trefuse</div>\n<div>\n\t英[rɪˈfjuːz; ˈrɛfjuːs] 美[rɪˈfjuz; ˈrɛfjus; ˈrɛfjuz]</div>\n<div>\n\tv. 拒绝；不肯；不愿<br />\n\tn. 废物，垃圾<br />\n\tadj. 无用的</div>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15632/item/793948/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n\t&nbsp;</p><br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p516751/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p516751\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p517874/\">美剧中的亚洲面孔 你认得出他们吗?</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518419/\">时尚贴士：怎样穿衣服最显瘦</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p519168/\">乔治王子长这样？电脑合成少年照</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p517448/\">十分钟改变法：十分钟就能做好的事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518729/\">破产姐妹笔记105：爷们点英语怎么说</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p427945/\">从零基础到英语达人：新概念帮你轻松搞定！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p519070/\">总是觉得累？7个小贴士恢复活力</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p517619/\">智慧的声音：8句发人深省的名言</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p518035/\">英国小王子首亮相 “还好长得像妈妈”</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=